321 2045 378 (        specified in 16.2.) 378 SB
321 2145 435 (PROPOSED WORDING:) 435 SB
321 2245 151 (    2.8p1:) 151 SB
321 2345 1165 (        The sequences in both forms of header-names are mapped in an) 1165 SB
321 2395 1172 (        implementation-defined manner to headers or to external source) 1172 SB
321 2445 609 (        file names as specified in 16.2.) 609 SB
