321 2645 416 (CURRENT WORDING:) 416 SB
321 2745 183 (    3.4.5p1:) 183 SB
321 2845 1034 (        the unqualified-id is looked up in the scope of the object) 1034 SB
321 2895 278 (        expression.) 278 SB
