321 245 1240 (The current wording makes it sound as if a member deallocation function) 1240 SB
321 295 1202 (with the parameters \(void*, size_t\) cannot ever be generated.  This was) 1202 SB
321 345 1148 (not the intent, simply that such a generated function would never be) 1148 SB
321 395 1206 (used as the "usual" \(non-placement\) deallocation function.  The revised) 1206 SB
